snippet.title: "Magical girls on strike!"~ Hero Hours Contract (Kickstarter Trailer)
snippet.description:
Currently on Kickstarter: http://kck.st/308bFzM

Magical Girls are real... but the pay SUCKS.

Hero Hours Contract is a tactical puzzle game about underpaid magical girls and their fight to become unionised!

Coming soon for Nintendo Switch, PC and Mac.

Follow for updates: https://twitter.com/SOGormanGames

Trailer music by DDRKirby(ISQ): https://ddrkirbyisq.bandcamp.com/
